    <character name="Man-at-arms">
        <description>
            <race>Human</race>
            <age>16</age>
            <short>
                The man-at-arms is a foot soldier in the employ of his lord.
            </short>

            <background>
                <para>
                    You are a freeman who has given up a life of farming
                    to spend it instead fighting full time for your lord.
                    You have been provided with basic weapons and armour,
                    and are expected to be available for the defence of
                    your lord's land at any time.
                </para>

                <para>
                    When times are quiet, you may help out in the fields,
                    or even sell your skill at arms to others, though you
                    do not consider yourself a full time mercenary.
                    Working as a caravan guard for local freemen, guard
                    duty and patrol are the most excitement you normally
                    see.
                </para>
            </background>
        </description>

